    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🦾 Giant Mechs × Space Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pilot a humanoid mech and soar freely through outer space. Engage enemies from every direction using full 3D tactical movement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/230b60d08d984cab59ab6aec2f39bed3.poster.avif?t=1762257681\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/230b60d08d984cab59ab6aec2f39bed3.webm?t=1762257681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/230b60d08d984cab59ab6aec2f39bed3.mp4?t=1762257681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎯 Auto-Aim FPS for Instant Action</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep enemies centered on your screen to auto-lock and fire. Master inertia-based movement to chase down fast-moving targets. Show your piloting skills by mastering motion in zero gravity!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/3b41c40105b84c10c63764b3d9fa0029.poster.avif?t=1762257681\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/3b41c40105b84c10c63764b3d9fa0029.webm?t=1762257681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/3b41c40105b84c10c63764b3d9fa0029.mp4?t=1762257681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💥 Slash, Shoot, Explode — Master Four Sub-Weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missiles, grenades, beam blades, and shields. Switch weapons on the fly to control the battlefield. Your mech is built for both close-quarters and long-range combat. Note: This title does not feature mech customization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/e5d37b08cdac150f408c917672cd1768.poster.avif?t=1762257681\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/e5d37b08cdac150f408c917672cd1768.webm?t=1762257681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/e5d37b08cdac150f408c917672cd1768.mp4?t=1762257681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📖 Simple Story, Snappy Missions</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re a rookie pilot, thrown into a space war for your homeland. Join a rough-edged strike squad and survive the front lines. A short sci-fi narrative connects 12 high-paced missions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/3525f94a0a0591e0b4328a0098f5b835.poster.avif?t=1762257681\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/3525f94a0a0591e0b4328a0098f5b835.webm?t=1762257681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/3525f94a0a0591e0b4328a0098f5b835.mp4?t=1762257681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛰️ Coordinate Military Ops with Your Squad</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow your commander’s orders and move fluidly through battle. Support allied warships, defend key points, and adapt to a shifting battlefield. Tactical awareness is key to survival in this space shooter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/693da59b75c8596ced166dcb083113e8.poster.avif?t=1762257681\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/693da59b75c8596ced166dcb083113e8.webm?t=1762257681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123770/extras/693da59b75c8596ced166dcb083113e8.mp4?t=1762257681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
